# NEXT STEPS

For my next steps into making this project better, since I will be continuing to work on it, I will think about many new things I
can add to the project to make it better. The first thing I could do is modify the systems of control. As of right now I am using a
wireless remote controller, but in the future I would like to use some sort of interactive design. The first thing I can think of
right now it is using a glove with a gyroscopic sensor and flex sensors for the new controls. It will still operate wirelessly.
Now the included gyroscopic sensor will detect angles from its user's hand and translate them into degrees of motion, like the
joystick design. The flex sensors will move the gripper and maybe the wrist construction when flexed in and out. Although there are many
things that I could add to this project; I am extremely happy with how it turned out as of now, and I'll be even more so when the new
additions come along. 
